Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, fuse3
Description: Fault-tolerant replicated filesystem facade built on FUSE3
 chiron3fs mirrors filesystem operations to multiple replica directories
 through a single mounted facade filesystem.

